        </div> 


            
        <div class="downloads-content">

                <p>Connect the unit to the PC using a USB cable.&nbsp; If the USB drivers 
				        have not yet been installed, you will have an opportunity to do so now. 
				        Please click <a target="_blank" href="/pages/inline-speedometer-usb-driver-installation">here</a> for USB driver installation Instructions. You may have to wait 
				        4-5 seconds for the PC to recognize the unit.</p>
        
