    <div class="content-card-next">


        <div class="section-title">
        <span>Step 5: Program the unit </span>
        </div> 


            
        <div class="downloads-content">

                        <p>Click on the <b><i>Program</i></b> button.&nbsp; The <b><i>Status</i></b> 
				        field at the bottom will indicate the status of the programming session.&nbsp; 
				        It should take only 4-5 seconds to program the unit.&nbsp; Upon 
				        completion, the <b><i>Status</i></b> field will say either “Success” or 
				        “Error”.&nbsp; If the status is “Success”, you are done and can disconnect 
				        the unit from the PC and install it in the vehicle.&nbsp; If the status 
				        was “Error”, the programming session was unsuccessful, and you can either 
				        attempt to program again (without disconnecting the unit from the PC), or 
				        you can contact Hypertech for support.</p>
           

